Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're beginning to understand\Nthat I'm way out of your league!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Strongest in the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the Flame Alchemist is stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's just had it easy all his life.\NNo real challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ed.\NYou know it's not cool picking on a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Weakling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't won yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you! I'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Such classic bad guy lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well you'd better remember,\Nbecause my memory stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later. It's naughty, Shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a super small\Nsuper shorty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
